  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You perform a series of insanely fast strikes so fast that your fists grow hot from the resistance of the air around them. You lock yourself in place, and cannot move from the space you cast this jutsu in. Make 5 melee Taijutsu attacks. On a hit, you deal [Unarmed damage].</p><p>The strain of this jutsu causes you to suffer blowback from each successful strike. You take 1d6+1 necrotic damage that cannot be reduced or resisted or reacted to for each successful attack you land.</p>",
